com.opengamma.strata.function.marketdata.curve

Class DiscountCurveMarketDataFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.function.marketdata.curve.DiscountCurveMarketDataFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MarketDataFunction<Curve,DiscountCurveId>

    public class DiscountCurveMarketDataFunction
extends Object
implements MarketDataFunction<Curve,DiscountCurveId>
    Market data function that locates a discount factors curve.

    This function finds an instance of Curve that can be used to determine discount factors in the currency held in DiscountCurveId.

    The curve is not actually built in this class, it is extracted from an existing CurveGroup. The curve group must be available in the MarketDataLookup passed to the build(com.opengamma.strata.market.id.DiscountCurveId, com.opengamma.strata.calc.marketdata.CalculationEnvironment, com.opengamma.strata.calc.marketdata.config.MarketDataConfig) method.
